  "kind": "Definition",
  "title": "Bound and Free Occurrences",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "An occurrence of a variable $x$ in a formula $\\varphi$ is \\emph{bound} if it\nlies within the scope of a quantifier $\\forall x$ or $\\exists x$.\n\nAn occurrence of $x$ is \\emph{free} if it is not bound by any quantifier in\n$\\varphi$.",
